      "module_path": "task_contract_reader",
      "docs": "Filesystem secondary adapter implementing usecase::pre_review_gate::TaskContractReaderPort. Reads <items_dir>/<track_id>/task-contract.json, decodes it via task_contract_codec::decode, and returns a domain::task_contract::TaskContractDocument. The items_dir is injected at construction time (stored as a private PathBuf field) so callers do not need to pass it on every read call. Missing file maps to PreReviewGateError::TaskContractNotFound; I/O and codec errors map to PreReviewGateError::TaskContractReadFailed.",
